          revolutionize the way students engage with one another on a college
          campus. Every day each student receives information from the school
          and from one another via multiple different platforms. Whether that's
          an email about a school event, a GroupMe message from your dorm RA, a
          facebook post about housing, textbooks being sold on instagram, sports
          news on Twitter, text messages, canvas notifications... the list goes
          on and on!
        </p>
