      <section id="news">
        <h2>News</h2>
        <p>
          After Tim's spring semester abroad in Spain was canceled due to
          COVID-19, he and a few of his friends decided to relocate for the
          semester and take advantage of online classes. As someone who is
          immunocompromised, Tim decided that it would be safer to escape the
          crowded and reckless BC off-campus neighborhood and find a place in
          the U.S. where he could avoid the virus and recreate his anticipated
          adventures abroad. As a result, Tim is currently taking classes in
          Oahu, Hawaii!
        </p>
